Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.53,0:00:04.23,bitoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(439,372)}-2年前 西伯利亚-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 在哪 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:22.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在流星坠地之前把愿望说三遍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.13,0:00:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个愿望就会实现 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是日本的民间巫咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前从你妈妈那里听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有变成美女的巫咒或长个子的巫咒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在许什么愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现流星就意味着有人死去 这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.56,0:00:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.85,0:00:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少能看到真正的星空的时候 这只是个传说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.63,0:01:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.07,0:01:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.23,0:01:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.72,0:01:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.22,0:01:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是两年前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.01,0:02:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那个被称为「东京大爆炸」事件发生的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.08,0:02:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑成为了契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.31,bitoshi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(439,372)}-2年后 符拉迪沃斯托克-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就香烟的烟来说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二手烟比一手烟的有害物质更多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高致癌性的二甲基亚硝胺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一手烟的含量为5.3-43微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而二手烟的含量则为680-823微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喹啉含量在二手烟里的含量则是一手烟的11倍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约还有18000微克
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样 要俄罗斯人不吸烟也是绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管大家都知道 理性的思考来说最好还是戒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是除非变成传说中的契约者 不然就无法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.24,0:03:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 有听过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些星星陨落是因为有契约者死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.49,0:03:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的存在吗 那样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的话想见识下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别拿我开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是危险分子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.18,0:03:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦的事情已经够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一杯1968年的格伦荻佛龙 纯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.88,0:03:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窖藏了33年的雪利酒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在这家店的滞销品里发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人 您怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是April吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是August7
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为魔术师的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经向俄罗斯当局透露了情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FSB两天后会进行搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}FSB 俄罗斯联邦保安局
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了收集好的数据外都放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,July呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.67,0:04:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.59,0:04:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你经常和苏芳在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在关注你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都很在意你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那不是尼卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可能脑袋不聪明而且老是打架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我一定会好好珍惜你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好珍惜你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是告白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办 怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗 和我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 真的行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:05:58.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可以一起回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.26,0:06:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.01,0:06:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是肯定的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 我不是故意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然 偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 那个照相机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 等下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为塔尼亚当时的表情很漂亮我才拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是苏芳 这样子行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为尼卡是苏芳的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.14,0:06:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和尼卡只是同一个摄影俱乐部的会员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会喜欢那粗野的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然老是和我吵嘴 比我高年级还幼稚的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没什么品味
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却很意外的对小孩子很温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很不错的人哦 我可以保证
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 别再说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳 塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天轮到你们打扫卫生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界往往在那么一夜之间就改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.44,0:07:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱是什么我现在还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.93,0:07:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我知道 塔尼亚已经迎来了那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没有见过真正的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,13年前那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然东京和巴西各出现了一道「门」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京的那道门被称为「地狱之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴西的那道门被称为「天国之门」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「门」的附近出现了没见过的事物和现象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且任何人都无法接近那里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太引人注目了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的啊 这个镜头没有微距的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小裤裤全露出来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有穿裤袜没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.84,0:08:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思的是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个世界变了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也引发了大规模的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这一带很少受战争的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但变化却无时无刻不在进行着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.63,0:09:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野猫而已啦 瞄上佩恰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士今天也很忙 在研究所那边不回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了很丰盛的晚饭 来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.82,0:09:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 贝拉 听我说 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天塔尼亚被告白了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被谁 被谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是尼卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.48,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼卡不是苏芳的男朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那苏芳也有喜欢的人喽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着「门」的出现 真正的星空消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.39,0:10:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们所看到的只是虚假的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.48,0:10:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.63,0:10:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片天空中的星星是契约者的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我哦 进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一种很难理解的感情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然谁都知道这只是因荷尔蒙分泌所引发的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而人却想将其当作一种寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很美妙的感觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.45,0:11:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得能够像你这样拥有梦想是件很美妙的事 苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 把我当傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是梦终究会醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像爸爸和妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啦 妈妈的写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.36,0:11:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来妈妈过的还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.10,0:11:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找个时间 我们去看妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去日本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 这...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.27,0:11:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于现在的我来说 妈妈只是一个毫无意义的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是叫你不要在那房间呆太久吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑是我的弟弟啊 双胞胎弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.19,0:12:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是姐弟还是家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都和紫苑无关
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法理解这一点的话 你早晚会受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是一家人 为什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.75,0:12:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还拿着这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.21,0:12:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在等着啊...所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要继续做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间只会朝前流逝 永远无法倒退
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者没有心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 佩恰你如何认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩恰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:06.72,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(364,464)}第一话 黑猫是不会梦见星星的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.38,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界往往在那么一夜之间就改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.18,0:13:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何前兆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少见啊 你竟然迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅 塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅举止有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晨你约好一起上学 你也没来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我做了什么惹你生气的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到这是无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无意义？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有打算为你生小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便做这样的事也没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是为了这个而告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.82,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不放手的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朗塞尔诺福特辐射光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契 契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.41,0:15:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转变成契约者没有任何征兆 是突然的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.08,0:15:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性格和行为方式发生天翻地覆的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且一定会引起骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快会被国家机关监禁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:29.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且把周围的人的关于契约者的记忆消除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用爸爸研究的ME
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}ME MemoryEraser（记忆消除）的略称
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔尼娅 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.01,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑 怎么到这儿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这座房子里不是修了许多秘密通道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让爸爸和我在遇到危险的时候都能立即逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代价已经支付过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来 到我的房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始 研究所的所有东西都被冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不许碰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换上衣服 我的衣服不会那么显眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是护身符哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:30.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定记得带上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.81,0:17:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄丢的话 我们肯定还能再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.89,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往研究所的方向去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉知道逃出去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.97,0:17:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉? 怎么回事 紫苑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.95,0:17:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他们不是在追我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许提问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:17:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搜查的来了 准备逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解 按照预定顺序进行回收
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收的顺序是紫苑 博士 资料
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一目标消失 似乎已经逃脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,July 知道行踪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 那个房间里没有玻璃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 博士的房间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑 还是FSB
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不是 是个成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东洋人 戴着假面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假面?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,April 被窃听了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.98,0:18:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后封锁无线 按照C计划执行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.29,0:18:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提问的人是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星的碎片在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.08,0:18:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你就没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有呕吐物和其他的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是隶属于MI6的April
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑 到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么博士会被杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苏芳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫苑呢 紫苑在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.89,0:20:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了 能请你跟我走一趟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.13,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实的话 可以分一点给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是代价 我也不是那么想吃这些东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.99,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天肌肉又要痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约者吗 真是麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.42,0:23:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BK 201
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从虚假的天空中 流星陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬的闪光却是生命的消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.82,0:24:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤红的火焰让以往的羁绊消失于无形
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.45,0:24:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切燃尽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.37,0:24:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的刀刃贯穿心脏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.45,0:24:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女孤身一人在寒冷的城市中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.36,0:24:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨落的星辰无法再次发出光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.98,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能化为一片漆黑 等待着腐朽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.99,0:24:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍将有流星陨落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.94,0:24:27.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:29.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.94,0:24:31.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:14.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}暮れてく　夕映えに背中押されて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:14.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}黑夜渐渐袭来 晚霞映照在背脊上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:24.78,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}歩き出す　影が示す方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:24.78,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}朝着影子指示的方向迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:38.08,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}絶えない　いくつもの出会いと別れを繰り返し
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:38.08,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不断重复着无数次的相逢离别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.61,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこへ向かうのか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.40,0:22:40.61,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}到底要去往何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:45.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}人は誰も迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.94,0:22:45.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论谁都彷徨迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.37,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}罪と言う名の定めを背負って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:50.37,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}即使背负着罪恶之名的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:59.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}それでもなお　生きる意味を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:59.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仍然明白生存之意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:04.00,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕らは　So day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:04.00,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们 So day by day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:11.11,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}明日へ続く道の途中で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.34,0:23:11.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}在通往未来的道途中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.90,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Now say it again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:13.90,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Now say it again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:27.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君と二人のまま　いられなら　いいのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.15,0:23:27.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能这样和你在一块就好了
